{"type": "article", "id": 26660, "title": "房子造型的月历", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-11T06:44:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702150559ZfVmYATKc2oNI8eE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">“亲爱的月历君，你想成为什么？”AutoCAT 日历设计研究中心找到的答案是：变成一座房子。这样的变身为普通的纸质月历增添了一股乐趣，让人更愿意将它们摆在桌头。透过窗户还专门标出了比较重要的日子，月份的标示则隐藏在每座房子门口。就像是俄罗斯套娃那样，这 12 座房子还可以套在一起，让你不需要担忧它们会不会太占地方。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150557grv0ZwO42QG7sBpJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215055729Ldn8uNxwm5QlFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150558c2xPgJR9wp6FZHvX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150558WVZCqzNAiHL4cYSf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}